mutation ($payload:NfcCreateTagInput!)
{
	nfcCreateTag (payload:$payload)

		id
		code
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		urlBase
		params
		offset
		isSessionRequired
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

graphql.query:
query ($query:[QueryStatementInput])
{
	nfcGetTags (query: $query)
	{
		id
		code
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		urlBase
		params
		offset
		isSessionRequired
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:[QueryStatementInput])
{
	nfcFindTag (query: $query)
	{
		id
		code
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		urlBase
		params
		offset
		isSessionRequired
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	nfcFindTagById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		code
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		urlBase
		params
		offset
		isSessionRequired
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:NfcUpdateTagInput!)
{
	nfcUpdateTag (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		code
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		urlBase
		params
		offset
		isSessionRequired
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
{
	nfcDeleteTagById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		code
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		urlBase
		params
		offset
		isSessionRequired
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:[QueryStatementInput])
{
	nfcDeleteTags (query: $query)
	{
		id
		code
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		urlBase
		params
		offset
		isSessionRequired
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
